Down town there has been a rising fear 
of crime and activity and secret intelligence 
has recently found that a possible attack could
take place at the famous Victoria Park or the 
Multi-Billion Pound Bank Consumer. A Specialized 
squad has been sent in to prevent these possible
actions.
As a Terrorist You must Ensure you Plant C4 Explosives 
Either In Victoria Park or In the Central Area of the
Bank
As a Counter-Terrorist You must Prevent and Secure 
These Two Areas At all Cost, Failure Could result in
deadly consequences.
